Tarastia is a lesser goddess of Law, Order, Truth, Justice, and Just Vengeance worshiped in Mystara. She is a patroness of the Thyatian empire. 
She dwells in Arvenna, the Chanting Grounds, along with the demigoddess Mayaheine.
Sources: Dawn of the Emperors boxed set, Hollow World boxed set, Wrath of the Immortals, Warriors of Heaven